snippet: The investigation involves the behavior of workers who were close to Gov. Scott Walker when he was executive of Milwaukee County.
abstract: The investigation involves the behavior of workers who were close to Gov. Scott Walker when he was executive of Milwaukee County.
lead_paragraph: Scott Walker, the Republican governor of Wisconsin, will meet with a prosecutor who has been investigating the behavior of workers in his previous public office, at the helm of Milwaukee County, Mr. Walker's campaign office said Friday.

headline.main: Wisconsin Governor Is to Meet With Prosecutor
